The Dennis Prager Radio Show DEC-18-2013 WED..............PODCAST




Dennis Prager Radio Show



Prager 20131218  3 Days of God

Prager H3: Dennis covers the top stories of the day and is joined
              by James Buchan, investigative journalist,

         His new book is Days of God: The Revolution in Iran and Its Consequences.

Prager 20131218  1 What Color Is Santa?

Prager H1: A faux debate is raging: 

               Is Santa white?

                   Dennis struggles to deal seriously with this absurd issue,
                     but he manages to do it, and explain the Left in the process
